<p>2006届软件技术专业毕业生校友张成龙生向母校和辛勤工作的老师们表达了最衷心的感谢和最崇高的敬意。他向即将踏上人生新征程的2023届毕业生们分享了自己的心得体会。</p><p><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-06-25%2018%3A34%3A26%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8722.png?Expires=2003049267&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=h74HVZc%2B0IcwJxKkLbZ9biJk0UE%3D" alt="" width="450" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); text-indent: 42.6667px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: block; width: 450px; height: 284px;" height="284" border="0" vspace="0" title=""/></p>